 SDS. Three regimes of destabilization\nare found to exist depending on the ionic strength of the aqueous phase. They\ncorrespond to the prevalence of: 1) solubilization/ripening, 2) aggregation,\nand 3) crystal precipitation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2020 00:13:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-23"}
