 thereby improving the short-range\nelectron-electron correlation in metallic densities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2020 00:57:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Oct 2020 00:41:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-25"}
