ular\ndistances, owing to their small size and large spin of the rare earth ion in\nthe molecule.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2020 11:08:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 Jul 2020 07:34:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 20 Feb 2021 10:36:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 3 Jun 2021 05:14:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-23"}
