 and temporal contrast conditions using a\nstate-of-the-art high-repetition rate PW laser system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2020 15:38:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 27 Sep 2020 21:13:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Mar 2021 14:17:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-08"}
